<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Neuenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Rückzahlung des vom Zöllner zu Neuenburg entgegen altem Herkommen von Thomas Vischer, Diener des Kaufmanns Hans Stark, Bürger zu Nürnberg, erhobenen Zolls.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_168" id="83v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_168_r1l1">Der Stat cʒu <expan>VVeliſchen<ex>n</ex>ewb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_168_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat fürgelegt Hans Stark 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger </del> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_168_r1l3">ſeinen vnd ~ <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> geſellſchaft vvegen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_168_r1l4">Thomas Viſcher Jr diener geſagt vnd cʒu vviſſen getan hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_168_r1l5">daʒ der Cʒollner beẏ ew cʒu <expan>Newb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> von Jm cʒol geuordert hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_168_r1l6">den Er Jm auch <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müſte vnd Jm den <expan>eıngeantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hab / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_168_r1l7">Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>Cʒolln<ex>er</ex></expan> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvillen daran vveẏſen wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_168_r1l8">daʒ Er <expan>de<ex>n</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſere<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>burger<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒol widergeb / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_168_r1l9">eʒ dabeẏ <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſſe als das von <expan>alterherkume<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_168_r1l10">cʒollfreẏ beẏ ew ſein / als Jr das ſelber vvol wiſʒt / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_168" id="83v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu <expan>Welischen<ex>n</ex>ewb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Hans Stark von seinen und
                                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> gesellschaft wegen,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie daz im Thomas Vischer, ir diener, gesagt
                        und czu wissen getan hab, daz der czollner bey ew czu
                            <expan>Newb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> von im czol gevordert hab, den er im
                        auch <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müste und im den
                                <expan>eingeantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hab.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>czolln<ex>er</ex></expan> durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen
                        daran weysen wöllet, daz er <expan>de<ex>n</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>unsere<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>burger<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czol widergeb und ez dabey
                                <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lasse, als das von <expan>alter
                                herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        czollfrey bey ew sein, als ir das selber wol wiszt. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
